    "en": {
      "title": "Mannar Madu Annai's Adi Festival is a special place",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mannar Madu Annai's Aadi festival took place today (2) Saturday morning.",
        "Following the New Day services, a joint Mass was offered on Saturday morning.",
        "Under the leadership of Mannar Diocese Bishop Emmanuel Fernando Andagai, Jaffna Diocese Bishop Jasrin Penat Gnanaprakasam and priests jointly offered the festival mass.",
        "After the Mass, Thirucharupa Bhavani took place and devotees were blessed with Thirucharupa.",
        "It is also noteworthy that lakhs of devotees come from many parts of the country to seek the grace of Mother Madu."
      ],
